what other people are saying.

280
00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:47.720
Amanda is definitely on my mind.

281
00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:48.880
What's your motive here?

282
00:14:48.880 --> 00:14:52.120
Why are you so strongly pushing
people to think a certain way

283
00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:55.920
