285
00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:01.560
PEACOCK CAWS

286
00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:06.280
- I think it's Stephen...
- Yeah.
- Yeah.
- ..Roxy...

287
00:15:06.280 --> 00:15:08.040
- Yeah.
- ..and Jade.

288
00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:10.480
The thing with Stephen -
he was bright red when he come in.

289
00:15:10.480 --> 00:15:11.640
- Yeah. no. it's true.
- I know he...

290
00:15:11.640 --> 00:15:14.080
- No. no. no. it's true.
- He was in that room with me.

291
00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:16.240
- Ben. Ellie. James.
