- Fire - playing with fire.

330
00:17:21.040 --> 00:17:22.160
Planes with fire?

331
00:17:22.160 --> 00:17:25.000
- Not "planes"! Playing.
- Playing!

332
00:17:26.920 --> 00:17:28.640
