454
00:23:20.440 --> 00:23:21.480
Reece!

455
00:23:25.160 --> 00:23:26.200
{\an8}Savage.

456
00:23:27.160 --> 00:23:28.720
I didn't know how to take it.
really.

457
00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:30.800
Is he just a really
clever Traitor now.

458
00:23:30.800 --> 00:23:32.920
